{"tid":2438753,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解numbers of係唔岩？","createTime":"2021-03-08T17:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T18:57:53.000Z","uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0372ef68d4d58d63ab73bb249248b41e71c0339","tid":2438753,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"我見好多地方都係咁用<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyd.gov.hk/en/tender_notices/contracts/prequalifications_and_tender_notices/2010/01HY2010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyd.gov.hk%2Fen%2Ftender_notices%2Fcontracts%2Fprequalifications_and_tender_notices%2F2010%2F01HY2010.html&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=b5e4427c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/en/tender_notices/contracts/prequalifications_and_tender_notices/2010/01HY2010.html</a><br />\n<br />\n  <code>Within the designated contract area, there are about 52,800 nos. of lighting points, 5,300 nos. of traffic bollards, 770 nos. of illuminated gantry signs and roadside directional signs, 360 nos. of footbridges and subways (about a total of 14,000 nos. of lighting points), 38 nos. of covered walkways/ferry concourses and amenity areas (about a total of 100 nos. of lighting points).</code><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s40069-012-0024-x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs40069-012-0024-x&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=d41ce836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s40069-012-0024-x</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">For each mix, 14 Nos. of 100 mm diameter by 200 mm high cylinders and 3 Nos. of 150 mmm cubes were cast in layers and the moulds were gently tapped with rubber mallet to provide minimum compaction. \n</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rashtrapatisachivalaya.gov.in/pro